------------------------------
* Compiling 
------------------------------

Requires OpenCV

mkdir build
cd build
cmake .. 

make -j4


--------------------------------
* Usage
--------------------------------
			
spm-slam:   program to use the proposed method. By default, the ARUCO_MIP_36h12 dictionary has been employed.
			It only requires two parameters. The video file, and the calibration camera file. The latter must be created with OpenCv or Aruco. 


	
The test data set employed in Sect 5.4 of the paper is in https://mega.nz/#F!zjJm2BxZ!i75Sx47APVmtjfUGm0R2ug

To evaluate the dataset, there is a script in folder spm			
		  


